I"’<p><em>Pauli Gerhardi Geistreiche Hauss- und Kirchen-Lieder</em> is a work by <a href="/authors/feustking_j">Johann Heinrich Feustking</a>, which includes the hymns of <a href="/authors/gerhardt_p">Paul Gerhardt</a> that were handed down to him from his son, Paul Friedrich Gerhardt. It is also notable as having included the <a href="/appendix/will">last will and testament</a> of Paul Gerhardt.</p>

